18:48.895 --> 18:51.898
- I did. I went out for drinks.
- Mm.

18:52.131 --> 18:54.167
I might go again tonight.

18:54.200 --> 18:56.769
Oh, yeah? I'm in.

18:56.803 --> 18:58.872
<i>Babcock! Quinones!</i>

19:07.447 --> 19:09.816
- Hey.
What's up, Sarge?

19:09.849 --> 19:11.484
Charmaine Grasa's
being transferred

19:11.518 --> 19:14.153
to the women's facility
in Framingham on Thursday.

19:14.187 --> 19:16.689
I want you guys
to transport her.

19:16.723 --> 19:18.291
Why us?

19:18.324 --> 19:20.860
Because this is our last shot
at getting her to cooperate.

19:20.894 --> 19:23.263
DA's trying to stack charges
against Frankie Cuevas,

19:23.296 --> 19:25.932
and we don't have him on the
narcotics without Charmaine.

19:26.165 --> 19:27.567
And if she's willing
to talk about New York

19:27.600 --> 19:29.269
while she's at it,
I'll take that, too.

19:29.302 --> 19:31.371
With all due respect,
she hasn't talked yet.

19:31.404 --> 19:32.672
And she's lawyered up.
It's just...

19:32.705 --> 19:34.207
That seems like
a waste of time.

19:34.240 --> 19:36.342
You afraid
of a long drive there, Trooper?

19:36.376 --> 19:37.610
No, sir.

19:37.644 --> 19:39.412
<i>Then you two pick
her up Thursday morning.</i>

19:39.445 --> 19:40.547
<i>You got it, boss.</i>

19:40.580 --> 19:42.482
That'll be all.

19:46.419 --> 19:47.620
<i>Ms. Segna,</i>

19:47.654 --> 19:49.722
<i>is it true
that when Sergeant Abruzzo</i>

19:49.756 --> 19:51.424
first approached you,
he solicited you

19:51.457 --> 19:52.592
for prostitution?

19:53.927 --> 19:55.895
- No.
<i>-That's odd.</i>

19:55.929 --> 19:58.631
I took those words
from your original statement.

19:58.665 --> 20:01.634
Well, is it true
that he leveraged his position

20:01.668 --> 20:03.403
as a police officer
to pressure you

20:03.436 --> 20:05.605
into an intimate relationship?

20:05.638 --> 20:07.407
No. That's not what happened.

20:07.440 --> 20:09.609
Do you understand that there
are consequences

20:09.642 --> 20:11.244
for lying to the police?

20:11.277 --> 20:13.279
<i>Ms. Segna gave information</i>

20:13.313 --> 20:15.848
that led to the arrest
of several high-value targets.

20:15.882 --> 20:18.651
As a result,
she was given immunity.

20:18.685 --> 20:20.486
Please don't make idle threats.

20:20.520 --> 20:22.422
Oh, but it's true.

20:22.455 --> 20:24.757
I did lie.

20:24.791 --> 20:26.926
And that's why I'm here now...

20:26.960 --> 20:29.596
to set the record straight.

20:29.629 --> 20:31.297
Why did you lie?

20:32.799 --> 20:36.603
I lied because Frankie Cuevas

20:36.636 --> 20:41.307
said that if I didn't do
exactly what he told me to do,

20:41.341 --> 20:42.976
he was gonna kill me.

20:44.577 --> 20:48.648
I lied because
I was afraid for my life...

20:50.283 --> 20:52.986
...and I was afraid
for my son's life.

20:54.687 --> 20:57.924
I lied because I had no choice.

21:00.793 --> 21:03.796
Ray Abruzzo...

21:03.830 --> 21:06.532
did not coerce me in any way.

21:06.566 --> 21:09.836
I seduced him,
and I was relentless.

21:11.671 --> 21:14.340
He was nothing but good to me.

21:16.376 --> 21:18.845
And then I let Frankie
ruin him.

21:20.847 --> 21:22.682
I ruined him.

21:24.484 --> 21:26.653
Thank you for your honesty.

21:41.768 --> 21:43.302
- Hey, hey.
<i>Hey.</i>

21:43.336 --> 21:45.538
- How did it go?
- Well...

21:47.607 --> 21:50.343
-...I crushed it.

21:50.376 --> 21:52.311
I, uh...
I cried and everything.

21:52.345 --> 21:53.446
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

21:53.479 --> 21:56.015
Told them Frankie
made me do it.

21:56.049 --> 21:57.850
What'd they say?

21:57.884 --> 21:59.752
Mm...

21:59.786 --> 22:04.357
all you need to know
is that I took care of it.

22:04.390 --> 22:06.693
I took care...

22:06.726 --> 22:07.760
of you.

22:09.662 --> 22:12.498
And now...

22:12.532 --> 22:14.567
I want you
to take care of me.

22:15.768 --> 22:18.738
What are you doing? Hmm?

22:18.771 --> 22:20.406
Don't you like it?

22:22.608 --> 22:24.644
I didn't know you talking
to the DA

22:24.677 --> 22:26.379
would make you
so fucking horny.

22:26.412 --> 22:28.781
Mm.

22:33.453 --> 22:35.088
My man's a cop.

22:37.757 --> 22:38.925
And that's hot.

22:41.461 --> 22:44.464
Mm.

22:44.497 --> 22:45.898
I'm not a cop yet, baby.

22:45.932 --> 22:47.133
You sure?

22:47.366 --> 22:48.634
Feels like you are.

23:18.931 --> 23:20.566
Answer it.

23:23.669 --> 23:25.538
Yeah, it's Abruzzo.

23:26.973 --> 23:28.107
Yes, sir.

23:31.911 --> 23:35.414
Yes, sir.
I'll be right over.

23:37.984 --> 23:39.418
Baby, we did it.

23:39.452 --> 23:42.088
We did it?

23:53.699 --> 23:55.168
Hey, I don't mean
to interrupt, but, uh...

23:55.201 --> 23:57.737
- Come on in.
- Take a seat.

24:00.907 --> 24:04.010
Well, the paperwork is still
being processed, but, uh...

24:05.912 --> 24:07.079
