24:09.515 --> 24:11.851
Congratulations, Sergeant.

24:14.220 --> 24:16.022
Sergeant.

24:19.058 --> 24:20.793
Getting my stripes back?

24:20.827 --> 24:23.162
Oh, I can't have my task force
headed up by a scrub, can I?

24:23.196 --> 24:24.597
Task force?

24:24.630 --> 24:26.499
We're setting up
on the New York connect,

24:26.532 --> 24:27.800
scoop the DEA.

24:27.834 --> 24:29.802
That's fantastic.

24:29.836 --> 24:31.137
Don't let me down, now.

24:31.170 --> 24:33.639
I went to bat for you,
and I expect big things.

24:33.673 --> 24:35.575
You're gonna get 'em, sir.

24:35.608 --> 24:37.610
All right, Andy,
I leave it to you.

24:41.047 --> 24:42.682
I'm on it, sir.

24:42.715 --> 24:45.017
Keep your nose clean, Ray.

24:51.023 --> 24:53.492
I know this is strange
meeting this way,

24:53.526 --> 24:55.561
but I just want you to know
that I appreciate--

24:55.595 --> 24:56.929
Just stop.

24:56.963 --> 24:59.966
Whatever voodoo bullshit
you pulled on Markson

24:59.999 --> 25:03.102
and everyone else,
it won't work on me.

25:03.135 --> 25:05.538
Just know time off
did me some good.

25:05.571 --> 25:07.707
I'm a new man.

25:07.740 --> 25:10.610
As soon as the paper clears,
you're back.

25:13.045 --> 25:15.214
Thank you, sir.
I won't let you down.

25:15.248 --> 25:18.618
One more thing...

25:18.651 --> 25:20.887
Since you're back at Sergeant,
Saintille's out.

25:20.920 --> 25:23.256
