the one to tell him.

25:23.289 --> 25:25.758
- What?
- We're only budgeted for one.

25:25.791 --> 25:27.260
Luckily, there's a spot
on the Body Side,

25:27.293 --> 25:29.061
so he's moving over.

25:29.095 --> 25:31.197
He should be in his office.

25:31.230 --> 25:34.000
I'm sure he'd rather hear it
from his old partner.

25:49.615 --> 25:50.683
<i>Hey, bud.</i>

25:50.716 --> 25:52.551
Hey, Ray Abruzzo, huh?

25:54.153 --> 25:56.722
Let me guess,
fucking did it, huh?

25:56.756 --> 25:57.957
Got your job back, right?

25:57.990 --> 26:00.092
Well, yeah, yeah, yeah.
Something like that,

26:00.126 --> 26:02.762
something like that.

26:02.795 --> 26:04.931
I'm coming back
as Sergeant, Alan.

26:04.964 --> 26:06.299
Congrats.

26:06.332 --> 26:07.867
And you're going
to Body Side.

26:15.141 --> 26:16.776
- What the fuck?
- It's not a demotion.

26:16.809 --> 26:18.611
It's not a demotion,
Alan, okay?

26:18.644 --> 26:21.580
You're still Sergeant.
It's a great fucking post.

26:21.614 --> 26:22.615
Wait.

26:22.648 --> 26:25.084
You fuck up and get fired

26:25.117 --> 26:27.987
and come back
at the same fucking level?

26:29.989 --> 26:31.590
That sounds about white.

26:33.159 --> 26:34.860
Ten years!

26:34.894 --> 26:38.030
Ten years I been on Dirty Side!
I built a fucking career here!

26:38.064 --> 26:39.699
But who gives a shit
about that?

26:39.732 --> 26:42.168
Not you! Not fucking Smith!

26:42.201 --> 26:44.737
Fucking expendable Alan!

26:44.770 --> 26:46.339
This some bullshit.

26:48.674 --> 26:50.710
I really wonder
what the fuck the difference is

26:50.743 --> 26:52.244
between me and you.

26:52.278 --> 26:53.679
Bro, it's not like that.

26:53.713 --> 26:54.981
Bro?

26:55.014 --> 26:57.750
Motherfucker, do you know
the quality of life

26:57.783 --> 26:59.051
on fucking Homicide?

26:59.085 --> 27:01.153
There's four detectives

27:01.187 --> 27:05.324
to cover every unattended body
on the goddamn Cape!

27:05.358 --> 27:07.326
They call you any time
day or fucking night.

27:07.360 --> 27:09.061
You see the worst
of the goddamn worst.

27:09.095 --> 27:11.764
And you got to make
whatever fucking shitty case

27:11.797 --> 27:14.200
that lands
on your goddamn desk!

27:14.233 --> 27:17.003
So it is like that, bro.

27:19.205 --> 27:20.940
I can't fucking believe
this shit.

27:20.973 --> 27:21.974
Right.

27:24.877 --> 27:28.014
Whoa, hey, hey.
What are you doing? Alan.

27:28.047 --> 27:29.749
You want your goddamn office
back, right?

27:29.782 --> 27:31.183
<i>-Hey, hey.</i>
- Shit.

27:31.217 --> 27:33.152
- Fuck.

27:33.185 --> 27:35.254
You know it doesn't have
to be this way.

27:35.287 --> 27:38.157
You're right. It doesn't.

27:38.190 --> 27:41.894
And knowing you,
it won't be this way for long.

27:43.829 --> 27:46.032
Keep it warm for me, Ray.

27:53.806 --> 27:56.709
You wasn't doing that
at physical therapy.

27:56.742 --> 27:58.844
Yeah, well, I needed that.

27:58.878 --> 28:01.847
- You needed it?

28:05.818 --> 28:07.887
I like this.

28:07.920 --> 28:09.889
Hmm.

28:09.922 --> 28:12.058
I like this a lot.

28:14.960 --> 28:16.429
No, baby.

28:18.731 --> 28:21.901
I can't. I got to take this.
I'm sorry.

28:32.945 --> 28:33.946
Yeah.

28:36.248 --> 28:38.317
Yeah, I know who this is.

28:38.350 --> 28:40.920
And I know you put up
for my bail.

28:42.254 --> 28:45.391
Yeah, I could get down
to New York.

28:45.424 --> 28:47.760
Shit, I was born ready.

28:50.396 --> 28:52.998
What was that about?

28:54.967 --> 28:56.469
You really want to know?

28:56.502 --> 28:57.903
If we're gonna do this,

28:57.937 --> 29:00.306
I need to know
what I'm getting myself into.

29:02.174 --> 29:03.309
All right.

29:05.444 --> 29:07.947
Well, how about we go
for round two,

29:07.980 --> 29:09.815
then I tell you everything?

29:21.961 --> 29:23.996
<i>Eddie Murphy.</i>

29:25.431 --> 29:28.000
<i>Oh, shit.</i>

29:28.033 --> 29:29.969
- So what'd you do this time?
<i>-Nothing.</i>

29:30.002 --> 29:31.170
I went to Dibby's,
and I happened to have

29:31.203 --> 29:32.938
an extra 99 cents in my pocket.

29:32.972 --> 29:35.941
And I wanted to see you
and the boat one last time.

29:35.975 --> 29:37.443
You miss it?

29:37.476 --> 29:40.312
Yeah. Of course I do.

29:40.346 --> 29:41.380
Will you?

29:41.413 --> 29:44.216
Probably. Yeah.

29:44.250 --> 29:46.085
<i>But fuck it.</i>

29:46.118 --> 29:48.087
I hear you got your bad guy.

29:48.120 --> 29:51.924
Yeah. Thanks, thanks.
It feels good, you know?

29:51.957 --> 29:53.259
I'm not just Crazy Jackie.

29:53.292 --> 29:54.827
Like, I can do
good things, too.

29:54.860 --> 29:57.563
Hey, I'm the only one
gets to call you crazy.

30:00.466 --> 30:01.934
Okay.

30:01.967 --> 30:04.136
So, uh, they're doing
this little retirement thing

30:04.170 --> 30:05.504
for me tomorrow.

30:05.538 --> 30:08.040
Um, can you make it?

30:08.073 --> 30:09.909
Uh, I mean, I got to...

30:09.942 --> 30:13.312
I got to check with my lady,
see if we're free.

30:13.345 --> 30:15.281
Hey, I'm fucking with you.

30:15.314 --> 30:18.184
Yeah, I wouldn't miss it
for anything. Come on.

30:24.223 --> 30:27.092
Yeah, I'm gonna miss you, too.

30:40.873 --> 30:43.609
- My man. Looking good.

30:43.842 --> 30:45.344
- I've been expecting you.

30:45.377 --> 30:47.846
Yeah. I wouldn't miss it
for the world.

30:47.880 --> 30:50.115
I mean, you, me, here...

30:50.149 --> 30:52.418
it's like the natural order
has been restored.

30:54.420 --> 30:57.223
- How's Renee?
- That's actually why I came.

30:57.256 --> 30:59.892
See, you and I both know you're
not getting out this time.

30:59.925 --> 31:02.561
So whatever little bullshit
threat you made to Renee,

31:02.595 --> 31:04.897
that's just you trying
to make yourself feel big.

31:04.930 --> 31:09.335
But she's a cop's girl now,
which means she's off-limits.

31:09.368 --> 31:12.104
And if you got threats,
you come to me.

31:12.137 --> 31:13.138
I got no beef with you.

31:13.172 --> 31:14.440
You know, I can't blame

31:14.473 --> 31:17.243
another man for falling
for the same shit as I did.

31:17.276 --> 31:20.112
She's a pretty girl.

31:20.145 --> 31:22.348
But how well
do you know her really?

31:22.381 --> 31:24.016
Do you know she used
to be a drug addict?

31:24.049 --> 31:25.417
I mean, are cops
even allowed to shack up

31:25.451 --> 31:27.052
with pill-popping
junkie whores?

31:27.086 --> 31:28.520
Watch your fucking mouth.

31:28.554 --> 31:31.624
Jorge underestimated her
and look what happened to him.

31:31.657 --> 31:34.560
Even I didn't see that coming.

31:34.593 --> 31:37.096
Oh, it's true.

31:37.129 --> 31:41.433
And with the piece I gave her
to protect herself at the club.

31:41.467 --> 31:43.435
Now they're charging me
with my own cousin's murder

31:43.469 --> 31:46.905
on top of those three kids
I had nothing to do with.

31:48.574 --> 31:52.111
But I guess that's on me
for trusting a murderous <i>puta.</i>

31:56.315 --> 31:57.650
See you at your trial, Frankie.

31:57.683 --> 32:01.954
In the meantime,
stay the fuck away from Renee.

32:01.987 --> 32:04.957
Bitch played you for a chump...

32:04.990 --> 32:06.625
again.

32:17.169 --> 32:18.337
Oh, shit.

32:26.278 --> 32:27.479
Oh, it's you.

32:27.513 --> 32:29.415
Yeah. What, you expecting
someone else?

32:29.448 --> 32:31.116
- Yes, actually.

32:31.150 --> 32:32.151
What's up?

32:35.421 --> 32:37.589
I got my job back.
That's what's up.

32:37.623 --> 32:38.957
- Are you serious?
- Yeah.

32:38.991 --> 32:40.659
I talked to
Lieutenant Smith last night.

32:40.693 --> 32:42.428
I'm coming back as Sergeant.

32:42.461 --> 32:44.463
Sergeant? So what,
you and Alan are both--

32:44.496 --> 32:46.298
Oh, he's going over
to Body Side.

32:47.499 --> 32:50.235
It's a lateral move.
It's no big deal.

32:50.269 --> 32:52.004
I thought you two were friends.

32:52.037 --> 32:55.507
He's fine.
He would do the same to me.

32:55.541 --> 32:56.709
Mm.

32:59.611 --> 33:01.647
All right,
well, look, anyway, um...

33:01.680 --> 33:04.049
I'm putting together
this New York task force.

33:05.718 --> 33:08.387
Are you...
are you asking me to be on it?

33:08.420 --> 33:10.189
Jesus, why do you got to make
things so fucking difficult,

33:10.222 --> 33:12.524
Jackie?

33:12.558 --> 33:15.361
Will you be
on my New York task force?

33:15.394 --> 33:17.496
Please?

33:17.529 --> 33:19.531
Sure.

33:19.565 --> 33:21.734
That why you came by?

33:21.767 --> 33:24.269
And one other thing...

33:24.303 --> 33:27.706
What specifically do you know
about Jorge Cuevas' murder?

33:27.740 --> 33:29.141
Why?

33:29.174 --> 33:30.409
Don't worry about it.

33:32.644 --> 33:35.214
All right.

33:36.548 --> 33:38.384
Ballistics came back
with a match on the .38

33:38.417 --> 33:41.153
Frankie had on him when
we picked him up at the club.

33:41.186 --> 33:43.021
And Jorge was buried
at the same place

33:43.055 --> 33:44.757
as Daisy and the pilot.

33:44.790 --> 33:46.325
- But...
- But what?

33:46.358 --> 33:48.460
Yeah. I don't know, man,
it's weird.

33:48.494 --> 33:51.764
Chuleta spilled about Daisy,
but he swears up and down

33:51.797 --> 33:53.532
that Frankie
wouldn't have killed Jorge.

33:53.565 --> 33:55.467
And they never found
a crime scene.

34:00.606 --> 34:04.076
Hey.

34:04.109 --> 34:06.378
Hi, Les.

34:06.412 --> 34:09.114
Leslie, Ray just said that
he's coming back as Sergeant,

34:09.148 --> 34:12.317
so we're all gonna be
working together soon.

34:14.620 --> 34:17.055
That's great. Congratulations.

34:21.326 --> 34:23.429
Okay, I'm out of here.

34:23.462 --> 34:26.098
Hey, Ray.

34:26.131 --> 34:28.600
No hard feelings, right?

34:28.634 --> 34:30.736
Sure.

34:34.606 --> 34:36.408
What the fuck?

34:36.442 --> 34:38.277
I know. I know. I know.
It's crazy.

34:38.310 --> 34:40.546
After everything,
after all that shit

34:40.579 --> 34:43.248
he brought down
on the department...

34:43.282 --> 34:46.785
Must be nice to be a dude,
just fail your way to the top.

34:46.819 --> 34:49.788
- Are you happy?

34:49.822 --> 34:51.723
I can't help it. I like him.

34:51.757 --> 34:54.626
That's because you're just
a big old softie.

34:56.662 --> 34:59.465
- Am I?
- Very, very soft.

35:17.115 --> 35:19.718
- Hey, buddy.
<i>Yeah.</i>

35:19.751 --> 35:21.620
I'm Sergeant Ray Abruzzo,
State Police.

35:21.653 --> 35:23.455
Let me ask you a question.

35:23.489 --> 35:26.758
Have you seen this girl, came
in right before Thanksgiving,

35:26.792 --> 35:28.360
would have looked
a little better than this?

35:28.393 --> 35:29.895
- Yeah. I remember her.
- You do?

35:30.128 --> 35:31.763
Mm, not too many chicks
come in here,

35:31.797 --> 35:35.767
none that look like that,
but, uh, she was looney tunes.

35:35.801 --> 35:37.669
Tried to buy one bullet,
like this is

35:37.703 --> 35:40.305
some kind of fucking
candy store or something.

35:40.339 --> 35:42.241
