of bullet?

35:42.274 --> 35:43.775
.38 caliber.

35:56.655 --> 35:59.858
<i>You hear Osito got out
the other day?</i>

35:59.892 --> 36:03.695
He must have given up something
big, 'cause he made bail.

36:03.729 --> 36:07.199
- Think it was you?
- Fuck off.

36:07.232 --> 36:09.334
I'm just thinking
out loud here,

36:09.368 --> 36:13.305
but what if, after
everything's said and done,

36:13.338 --> 36:15.574
you're the one left
holding the bag?

36:17.709 --> 36:19.711
We know you've been through
a lot, Charmaine,

36:19.745 --> 36:22.247
everything with your sister...

36:22.281 --> 36:23.682
it's horrible.

36:23.715 --> 36:26.184
<i>And I get it.</i>

36:27.920 --> 36:29.655
I even respect you
for not talking.

36:29.688 --> 36:30.822
It's honorable.

36:30.856 --> 36:32.391
Fuck honor.

36:32.424 --> 36:36.528
You really want to do time
for Frankie Cuevas?

36:36.562 --> 36:39.398
<i>You think he'd do
the same for you?</i>

36:39.431 --> 36:40.899
<i>We know you were
bringing the package</i>

36:40.933 --> 36:43.735
to Frankie when we caught you
on the bridge.

36:43.769 --> 36:45.938
Look, all you got to do
is get with your lawyer,

36:45.971 --> 36:47.739
